               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Wǝddāse Māryām “Praise of Mary” (fols. 1ra-8rb)
 II) ʾAnqaṣa
                     bǝrhān “The Gate of Light” (fols. 8rb-11vb)
 
 Additiones
                     1-3.</summary>
